  <meta name="flags" content="" />
  <meta name="assert" content="This test checks that anonymous table objects will be automatically generated by UAs if a table element is missing necessary sub-table elements (like table-row or table-cell). In this test, an anonymous table-row and one anonymous table-cell will be created around the inline content. The white space separating the 3 span elements should be preserved." />
  </head>

 <body>

  <p>There should be no red below, except for antialiasing issues.</p>

  <div style="position: relative; font-size: 2em;">
    <div style="position: absolute; z-index: 2; top: 0; color: green; display: table;">
    <span>a</span> <span>bc</span> <span>d</span>
   </div>
   <div style="position: relative; z-index: 1; color: red;">
   a bc d
   </div>
  </div>

 </body>
